{
  "stem": "26609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when the Germans came, he offered my mother to hide them in his church-- my mother, father, and youngest brother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All others were in Lwow, like my eldest sister, my brother, myself, younger sister-- two sisters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the youngest, Wolf, was with my parents, there, still.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was years later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he hid my mother in his church, in a cellar-- and my father and the youngest brother, Wolf-- during the German occupation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He fed them and kept him for quite-- I don't know exactly, because I haven't been there, but quite a number of months, since the beginning of the German occupation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At this time, the Germans didn't find out the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They didn't look for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "No one knew about the killings or other atrocities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But later-- the whole story, I found out from someone after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I didn't know about it, because I was in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Finally, they had a young-- they didn't have any chil-- that priest didn't have any children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The family consisted only of himself and a wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But there was a boy employed by him, to look after the-- he had some cows.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So he looked after the cows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That boy noticed once that the priest's wife carried downstairs some food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He have seen it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And most Gentiles said, if they find out about Jews and tell the Gestapo, you will be paid for it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He ran quickly to the Gestapo and told them that he's suspecting, at the church, some hidden Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then they came and got out my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They would probably have survived if not of that boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But they didn't send then Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That was at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "A few months later.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
